IN RE R.C. S234295 Supreme Court of California March 22, 2017

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 1/5. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for People v. Sanchez (2016) 63 Cal.4th 665, 204 Cal.Rptr.3d 102, 374 P.3d 320, is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, Rule 8.528(b).)
